Stage 3 — Answer Analysis Engine (v2)
•	Students answer actual CS questions inside Traceback
•	System analyzes wrong answers — not just scores
•	Error classification: concept error vs misunderstanding vs application error
•	Prerequisite mapping: if student fails recursion, check if they understand functions first
•	Confidence signals: fast wrong answers vs slow wrong answers
•	Forgetting curve detection: distinguish never learned vs learned and forgot

Stage 4 — AI Tutor Integration
•	Connect Gemini/Claude API for conversational tutoring
•	Student can ask 'why is my answer wrong?' and get a specific explanation
•	AI generates custom exercises for each student's exact gap
•	Real-time feedback on submitted answers
 
